This is the R-18 fantia contents of a twitter manga called A Parallel World With a 1:39 Male to Female Ratio Is Unexpectedly Normal. If you want context for the stuff going on here, go read the original manga over on mangadex and support the author. Also, I'm not the one translating/typesetting this, I'm simply uploading the contents from mangadex onto here. If there's a way to support the original scanner, do so on mangadex.

Author Kisa (きっさー):
https://twitter.com/kisa_kk
https://fantia.jp/fanclubs/484934
